                <div class="col-sm-9 text-justify">
                    <h3>MELODIE PRICE, RMT</h3>
                    <p>Melodie is a Registered Massage Therapist who graduated in 2007 from ICT Northumberland College in Halifax, Nova Scotia. She is a member of the Natural Health Practitioners of Canada (NHPC).</p>
                    <p>Her treatment methods include deep tissue massage, myofascial release and trigger point therapy. She has a special interest in sports &amp; injury rehabilitation as well as pregnancy massage. Melodie is very passionate about her work and likes to tailor each session to the individual needs of her clients.</p>
                    <p>Melodie is an avid runner, completed two half marathons with hopes to finish a full marathon in the near future. Her weekends are spent running, hiking, biking, and climbing.</p>
